description: Rose is back and living down at the beach with her new husband Manny Quinn. Charlie tries to talk to her but Rose tells him it?s best if he stayed away. Charlie then becomes consumed with trying to get Rose?s attention. He begins to stalk her. Finally Rose gives in and says she?ll meet with him. They begin a passionate affair. Jake and Eldridge do a take-off of the movie JACKASS and make their own movie called ?Dumbass.?
